f. Tree / Hierarchical Data Visualization (Simulated Treemap)
ğŸ“ Objective:
Group data into a hierarchy: Species â†’ PetalLength Range.
ğŸ“Š Steps in Tableau:
1.	Create a calculated field:
o	Go to Analysis â†’ Create Calculated Field
o	Name it: Petal Length Group
o	Formula:
IF [PetalLengthCm] < 2 THEN "<2"
